+        depends on DEBUG_KERNEL
+        depends on KPROBES
+        default n
+        help
+          This option provides for testing basic kprobes functionality on
+          boot. A sample kprobe, jprobe and kretprobe are inserted and
+          verified for functionality.
+
+          Say N if you are unsure.
+
